OL,3,CFamily of woman who went missing 12
OL,4,Cyears ago want death legally recognised
OL,6,FGeorge fears she may have come to
OL,7,Fharm, but accepts his family will now
OL,8,Falmost certainly never know what
OL,9,Fhappened to her.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's exceptionally
OL,12,Ffrustrating. I never imagined 12 years
OL,13,Fon, we wouldn't know what had happened
OL,14,Fto my great-aunt. But secondly, it's
OL,15,Fincredible to think that over 4 years
OL,16,Fafter applying to the courts for
OL,17,Fpresumption of death we're still
OL,18,Fwaiting.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
