OL,6,F"It's very puzzling that she got off
OL,7,Fin the Whitehawk district because
OL,8,Fthat's not where she lived. For many
OL,9,Fyears she lived in Bonchurch road.
OL,11,F"I do wonder if there was foul play
OL,12,Fbecause if there was an accident,
OL,13,Fsurely her body would have been
OL,14,Fdiscovered pretty quickly."
OL,16,FGiven Nellie's age at the time of her
OL,17,Fdisappearance, George wanted a court
OL,18,Fruling to declare her death.
