OL,3,CFamily of woman who went missing 12
OL,4,Cyears ago want death legally recognised
OL,6,FHe submitted the claim to the High
OL,7,FCourt's family division in 2024, but
OL,8,Fstill hasn't heard anything four years
OL,9,Fon.
OL,11,FGeorge said: "Every time I've enquired
OL,12,Fabout the progress of this
OL,13,Fapplication, I've been told I have to
OL,14,Fkeep waiting. I think it is an insult,
OL,15,FI think it's disgusting. I'm appalled
OL,16,Fto think that her memory is being
OL,17,Ftreated with such contempt."
