OL,6,FMr Holland said he will carry on his
OL,7,Fquest to bring legal recognition of
OL,8,FNellie's death and commemorate the
OL,9,Flife of someone he describes as
OL,10,Fvivacious, plucky, sociable and sorely
OL,11,Fmissed.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Sussex Police said:
OL,14,F"Our thoughts continue to be with the
OL,15,Ffamily and friends of Nellie Herriott
OL,16,Fwho was reported missing from Brighton
OL,17,Fin 2012.
OL,19,F"Sadly, despite an intensive
OL,20,Finvestigation, it remains unknown what
OL,21,Fhappened to her.
